{"tid":39010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Google 發表2016年最多人Search 時事人物","createTime":"2016-12-14T09:45:55.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T11:20:49.000Z","uid":731,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"58baa95dfb1becd19bb79560c120bba876a3558b","tid":39010,"uid":731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:45:55.000Z","msg":"Pokemon 同游蕙禎有啲乜嘢關係？相信就咁講，真係好難聯想到，兩者之間有啲乜嘢關係。如果問題改一改，問 Pokemon 同周柏豪有乜關係，網友就可能都仲聯想到比比鳥，但游蕙禎？真係諗唔到。諗唔到唔緊要，Google 話你知！即刻揭開 Pokemon 同游蕙禎之間的秘密！<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n原來，熱門遊戲《Pokemon Go》 同游蕙禎，雙雙都上左 Google 香港 2016 嘅搜尋排行榜！Google 每年一到年尾，就會做個統計，回顧番到底香港人在該年最關心的風雲人物、本地和國際大事、社會熱話、流行文化等等，旨在反映搜尋趨勢，了解有啲乜嘢關鍵字在過去一年迅速增加，而其搜尋量在一段時間內持續高企。而今年 Google 香港搜尋排行榜的結果如下:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.eprice.com.hk/nb/talk/1143/25076/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Fnb%2Ftalk%2F1143%2F25076%2F1&d=%2BnNreoHSAT5xh0CxqRKFY0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=f5bc556d\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.eprice.com.hk/nb/talk/1143/25076/1</a>"},{"pid":"28423cc95fc2658ce7c4664a50512eb33a0b11d1","tid":39010,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:46:31.000Z","msg":"xianggang<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef20d0368e8db6d349c5f58349a2a69bf37aa4bf","tid":39010,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:15:36.000Z","msg":"又Google港豬大法"},{"pid":"0bd5c5a427f4c73f3911ba0e4eb56d3251317499","tid":39010,"uid":13205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:19:38.000Z","msg":"標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又關pkm事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgm